div.row
 div.columns.small-3
  h1.home PIM
 div.columns.small-9.text-right
  button.small.fi-unlock(ui-sref="signin", ng-if="!isAuthenticated", title="Sign in")  Sign in
  button.small.secondary.fi-torso(ui-sref="signup", ng-if="!isAuthenticated", title="Sign up")   Sign up
  button.small.fi-lock(ui-sref="user.logout", ng-if="isAuthenticated")  Logout
div.row
 div.column.small-12
  h2.strong Personal Information Manager 
div.row
 div.column.small-12
  ul(style="list-style-type: none;")
   li.fi-calendar
    a(ui-sref="calendar.month")  Calendar
   li.fi-torsos
    a(ui-sref="contact.list")  Concacts
   li.fi-page
    a(ui-sref="post")  Posts
   li.fi-bookmark
    a(ui-sref="bookmark")  Bookmarks
div.row
 div.column.small-12
  h2.fi-lock  Access to your data
  p Keep your personal information private. Access your data wherever you are, whenever you need it, all under your control. 
   |Independent of Google, Facebook or other installed app/provider who can peek into your data.
  p Share items with Whatsapp, Telegram, SMS, Email, Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn 
    | via a sharelink and therefore completely independent of these providers.
  h2.fi-star  General features
  ul 
   li This 'Web App' has a responsive design so you can use it on your mobile, tablet or desktop. 
   li All data is (read only) available offline.
   li 
    a(href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/") Markdown is integrated 
    | so you can style your text easily.
div.row
 div.column.small-12
  h2.fi-calendar  Calendar
  ul
   li You can create events with the flag: <code>appointment</code> or <code>memo</code>. 
   li The calendar has month, week and day view. 
   li You can search events and swipe the calendar (left/right). 
   li Get reminders by e-mail.
  h2.fi-torsos  Contacts
  ul
   li Create contacts and add unlimited phonenumbers, companies, relations, e-mailaddresses, websites, addresses.  
   li Add birthdate and get a reminder by e-mail.
   li Add profile photos (crop and scale before upload)
   li Birthdate calendar view for contacts.
   li Download all contacts to vCard 3.0.
   li Download individual contacts to vCard 3.0.
  h2.fi-page  Posts
  ul
   li Create a post with the flag: <code>todo</code>, <code>note</code>, <code>blog</code> or <code>knowledge base</code>. 
   li Make a small note or a big article with Markdown. 
   li Auto-generate a table of contents (TOC) on a large articles. 
   li Search on keywords (title, content and tags).
   li Creat a pdf for sharing large posts created with Markdown.
  h2.fi-bookmark  Bookmarks
  ul
   li You can create a bookmarks with the flag: <code>media</code>, <code>fun</code>, <code>knowledge base</code>, <code>other</code>. 
   li Search on keywords (title, content and url).

